data.description: Nestled on 3+ acres  in the heart of Beach City, this exceptional home welcomes you to a world of luxury. Tailored for those seeking both comfort and elegance, this residence offers a host of remarkable features. Indulge in luxury with a gourmet kitchen, a spa-like primary retreat with a custom 17 ft shower, media room and a fully-furnished garage apartment like no other. Outdoor bliss is achieved with a resort-style pool, spa, an inviting palapa bar area, large covered deck, outdoor fireplace, and outdoor kitchen cater to your entertainment needs.  Not one but 2 homes. The fully furnished 2 bed/2 bath/office apt can be used for short/long term rental. Safety is paramount with double-reinforced walls, hurricane straps and cables. A 45 KW generator ensures the reliability of both the primary home and apartment. More than a house, this property offers the canvas for your  cherished memories. Contact us to discover this remarkable estate and make it your own. Your dream home awaits.
